#: mu/debugger/client.py:119
msgid "Connection timed out. Is your machine slow or busy? Free up some of the machine's resources and try again."
msgstr "Ulanish vaqti tugadi. Mashinangiz sekinmi yoki to'xtab qoldimi? Mashina resurslarining bir qismini bo'shating va qayta urinib ko'ring."

#: mu/debugger/client.py:133
msgid ""
"Could not find localhost.\n"
"Ensure you have '127.0.0.1 localhost' in your /etc/hosts file."
msgstr ""
"localhost topilmadi.\n"
"/etc/hosts faylingizda \"127.0.0.1 localhost\" mavjudligiga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:76
msgid "Select Mode"
msgstr "Rejim tanlash"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:80
msgid "Please select the desired mode then click \"OK\". Otherwise, click \"Cancel\"."
msgstr "Iltimos, kerakli rejimni tanlang va \"OK\" tugmasini bosing. Aks holda, \"Bekor qilish\" tugmasini bosing."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:101
msgid "Change mode at any time by clicking the \"Mode\" button containing Mu's logo."
msgstr "Mu logotipini o'z ichiga olgan \"Rejim\" tugmasini bosish orqali istalgan vaqtda rejimni o'zgartiring."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:140
msgid "When reporting a bug, copy and paste the content of the following log file."
msgstr "Xato haqida xabar berganingizda, quyidagi jurnal faylining mazmunini nusxalang va joylashtiring."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:164
msgid ""
"The environment variables shown below will be set each time you run a Python 3 script.\n"
"\n"
"Each separate enviroment variable should be on a new line and of the form:\n"
"NAME=VALUE"
msgstr ""
"Quyida ko'rsatilgan muhit o'zgaruvchilari har safar Python 3 skriptini ishga tushirganingizda o'rnatiladi.\n"
"\n"
"Har bir alohida muhit o'zgaruvchisi yangi qatorda va quyidagi shaklda bo'lishi kerak:\n"
"NAME=VALUE"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:189
msgid "Minify Python code before flashing?"
msgstr "Miltillashdan oldin Python kodini kichiklashtirasizmi?"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:194
msgid "Override the built-in MicroPython runtime with the following hex file (empty means use the default):"
msgstr "Quyidagi hex fayl bilan o'rnatilgan MicroPython mikrodasturini qoplaydi. (bo'sh ma'nolar sukut bo'yicha ishlatiladi):"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:220
msgid ""
"The packages shown below will be available to import in Python 3 mode. Delete a package from the list to remove its availability.\n"
"\n"
"Each separate package name should be on a new line. Packages are installed from PyPI (see: https://pypi.org/)."
msgstr ""
"Quyida ko'rsatilgan paketlarni Python 3 rejimida import qilish mumkin bo'ladi. Mavjudligini o'chirish uchun paketni ro'yxatdan o'chiring.\n"
"\n"
"Har bir alohida paket nomi yangi qatorda bo'lishi kerak. Paketlar PyPI (https://pypi.org/) dan o'rnatiladi."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:251
msgid "The folks at <a href='https://www.pythonanywhere.com/'>PythonAnywhere</a> make it easy for learners and educators to host simple web projects for free. You'll need to sign up for an account and provide the following details for Mu to deploy your web project."
msgstr "<a href=‘https://www.pythonanywhere.com/‘>PythonAnywhere</a> foydalanuvchilari o’quvchilar va o’qituvchilarga oddiy veb-loyihalarni bepul joylashtirishni osonlashtiradi. Veb-loyihangizni ishga tushirish uchun hisob qaydnomangiz uchun roʻyxatdan oʻtishingiz va Mu uchun quyidagi maʼlumotlarni taqdim etishingiz kerak boʻladi."

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:263
msgid ""
"\n"
"Copy your username on PythonAnywhere into here:"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"PythonAnywhere-da foydalanuvchi nomingizni bu yerga nusxalang:"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:267
msgid "username"
msgstr "foydalanuvchi nomi"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:273
msgid "Copy your <a href='https://www.pythonanywhere.com/account/#api_token'>secret API token from PythonAnywhere</a> into here:"
msgstr "Sizning <a href='https://www.pythonanywhere.com/account/#api_token'>PythonAnywhere-dan maxfiy API tokeni</a>ni bu yerga nusxalang:"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:281
msgid "secret api token"
msgstr "maxfiy api tokeni"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:286
msgid "Server location ('www' is a safe default):"
msgstr "Server joylashuvi (“www” xavfsiz standart hisoblanadi):"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:306
msgid "Automatically detect"
msgstr "Avtomatik aniqlash"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:336
msgid "Please select the language for Mu's user interface from the choices listed below. <strong>Restart Mu for these changes to take effect.</strong>"
msgstr "Quyida keltirilgan variantlardan Mu foydalanuvchi interfeysi uchun tilni tanlang. <strong>Ushbu o'zgarishlar kuchga kirishi uchun Mu-ni qayta ishga tushiring.</strong>"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:366
msgid "How to flash MicroPython to your device"
msgstr "MicroPython-ni qurilmangizga qanday yoqish mumkin"

#: mu/interface/dialogs.py:374
msgid "&nbsp;1. Determine the type of device (ESP8266 or ESP32)<br />&nbsp;2. Download firmware from the <a href=\"https://micropython.org/download\" style=\"color:#039be5;\">https://micropython.org/download</a><br/>&nbsp;3. Connect your device<br/>&nbsp;4. Load the .bin file below using the 'Browse' button<br/>&nbsp;5. Press 'Erase & write firmware'"
msgstr "&nbsp;1. Qurilma turini aniqlang (ESP8266 yoki ESP32)<br />&nbsp;2. Mikrodasturni <a href=\"https://micropython.org/download\" style=\"color:#039be5;\">https://micropython.org/download</a><br/>&nbsp;3 dan yuklab oling. Qurilmangizni ulang<br/>&nbsp;4. Quyidagi .bin faylini “Yuklash” tugmasi yordamida yuklang<br/>&nbsp;5. \"Mikrodasturni o'chirish va yozish\" tugmasini bosing"

