#: mu/logic.py:236
msgid "Hello, World!"
msgstr "Salom, Dunyo!"

#: mu/logic.py:238
msgid "This editor is free software written in Python. You can modify it, add features or fix bugs if you like."
msgstr "Ushbu editor Python tilida yozilgan bepul dastur hisoblanadi. Agar xohlasangiz, uni o'zgartirishingiz, funksiyalar qo'shishingiz yoki xatolarni tuzatishingiz mumkin."

#: mu/logic.py:241
msgid "This editor is called Mu (you say it 'mew' or 'moo')."
msgstr "Bu editor Mu (inglizchada \"mew\" yoki \"moo\") deb ataladi."

#: mu/logic.py:242
msgid "Google, Facebook, NASA, Pixar, Disney and many more use Python."
msgstr "Google, Facebook, NASA, Pixar, Disney va boshqalar Python’dan foydalanadi."

#: mu/logic.py:244
msgid "Programming is a form of magic. Learn to cast the right spells with code and you'll be a wizard."
msgstr "Dasturlash sehrning bir shaklidir. Kod yordamida to'g'ri afsun qilishni o'rganing va siz sehrgar bo'lasiz."

#: mu/logic.py:248
msgid "REPL stands for read, evaluate, print, loop. It's a fun way to talk to your computer! :-)"
msgstr "REPL qisqartmasi o'qish, baholash, chop etish, aylanish degan ma'noni anglatadi. Bu sizning kompyuteringiz bilan suhbatlashishning qiziqarli usuli! :-)"

#: mu/logic.py:251
msgid "Be brave, break things, learn and have fun!"
msgstr "Jasoratli bo'ling, narsalarni buzing, o'rganing va zavqlaning!"

#: mu/logic.py:252
msgid "Make your software both useful AND fun. Empower your users."
msgstr "Dasturingizni foydali va qiziqarli qiling. Foydalanuvchilaringizni quvvatlang."

#: mu/logic.py:253
msgid "For the Zen of Python: import this"
msgstr "Python Zen uchun: buni import qiling"

#: mu/logic.py:254
msgid "Diversity promotes creativity."
msgstr "Turli xillik ijodkorlikni rivojlantiradi."

#: mu/logic.py:255
msgid "An open mind, spirit of adventure and respect for diversity are key."
msgstr "Ochiq fikr, sarguzasht ruhi va xilma-xillikni hurmat qilish muhim ahamiyatga ega."

#: mu/logic.py:257
msgid "Don't worry if it doesn't work. Learn the lesson, fix it and try again! :-)"
msgstr "Agar u ishlamasa, tashvishlanmang. Darsni o'rganing, tuzating va qayta urinib ko'ring! :-)"

#: mu/logic.py:260
msgid "Coding is collaboration."
msgstr "Kodlash - bu hamkorlik."

#: mu/logic.py:261
msgid "Compliment and amplify the good things with code."
msgstr "Kod bilan yaxshi narsalarni  maqtang va kuchaytiring."

#: mu/logic.py:263
msgid "In theory, theory and practice are the same. In practice, they're not. ;-)"
msgstr "Nazariy jihatdan nazariya va amaliyot bir xil. Amalda, ular yo'q. ;-)"

#: mu/logic.py:266
msgid "Debugging is twice as hard as writing the code in the first place."
msgstr "Xatolarni topib tuzatish birinchi navbatda kod yozishdan ikki baravar qiyin."

#: mu/logic.py:267
msgid "It's fun to program."
msgstr ""

#: mu/logic.py:268
msgid "Programming has more to do with problem solving than writing code."
msgstr ""

#: mu/logic.py:269
msgid "Start with your users' needs."
