#: mu/interface/dialogs.py
msgid "Pico Firmware Flasher"
msgstr "Pico mikrodasturini yuklab qo'yish"

#: mu/interface/pico_flasher/dialog.py
msgid "How to flash MicroPython to your Pico"
msgstr "MicroPythonni Picoga qanday yozish mumkin"

#: mu/interface/pico_flasher/dialog.py
msgid ""
"1. Hold the <b>BOOTSEL</b> button on your Pico and plug it "
"into USB — it will appear as a drive called "
"<b>RPI-RP2</b> (or RP2350 for Pico 2).<br>"
"2. Click <b>Refresh Drive</b> until the drive is detected.<br>"
"3. Click <b>Fetch Versions</b> to load available firmware.<br>"
"4. Select a version and click <b>Download &amp; Flash</b>."
msgstr ""
"1. Picodagi <b>BOOTSEL</b> tugmasini bosib tuting va USBga ulang "
"— u <b>RPI-RP2</b> (yoki Pico 2 uchun RP2350) nomli disk sifatida paydo bo'ladi.<br>"
"2. Disk aniqlanguncha <b>Diskni yangilash</b> tugmasini bosing.<br>"
"3. Mavjud mikrodasturlarni yuklash uchun <b>Versiyalarni olish</b> tugmasini bosing.<br>"
"4. Versiyani tanlang va <b>Yuklab yozish</b> tugmasini bosing."

